query:
INSERT INTO watchlist (user_id, movie_id, movie_title, movie_poster, movie_type, movie_rating, added_from, created_at)
SELECT 
  user_id,
  movie_id,
  movie_title,
  movie_poster,
  movie_type,
  movie_rating,
  'swipe' as added_from,
  created_at
FROM saved_movies
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM watchlist 
  WHERE watchlist.user_id = saved_movies.user_id 
  AND watchlist.movie_id = saved_movies.movie_id
);
